        <blockquote class="u-text u-text-3">Food crisis has been faced a lot during these pandemic times. Thus, to minimise it, there are a lot more operations going on currently.First, we have the shiv thaali that has been introduced in the state since a long time now, can be a good option to inculcate in our website. Since, it costs very less, every person can afford it. This will help more people to know about it through our website and thus, help a lot more people. <br>Next, every day we need groceries, but we always don't get fresh vegetables and other groceries. Also, people affected with covid would need fresh food. Thus, we would be adding a vendors section in the website, where people would be able to contact directly to the vendors for fresh availability. This would surely benefit both the consumer and vendor.Lately,  many NGO's have come forward for food donations, food campaigns, services etc. Thus, we would be contacting such NGO's and display them on our website which will help people in multiple ways. Also, in emergency situations these NGO's can be asked for food donations in critical areas such as flood affected areas etc.
